OL,3,CConcerns raised as tiny plastic and
OL,4,Cfibreglass particles found in River
OL,5,CItchen
OL,7,FConcerns have been raised by
OL,8,Fresearchers after tiny plastic and
OL,9,Ffibreglass particles were found in
OL,10,FHampshire's River Itchen.
OL,12,FA study was carried out on the river
OL,13,Fby the University of Brighton and
OL,14,Fcitizen scientists from the Upper
OL,15,FItchen Restoration Community Interest
OL,16,FCompany (UIR CIC).
OL,18,FFewer than 300 chalk streams exist
OL,19,Fworldwide with England home to most of
OL,20,Fthem, including the River Itchen.
