OL,3,CConcerns raised as tiny plastic and
OL,4,Cfibreglass particles found in River
OL,5,CItchen
OL,7,FCitizen scientists from the local
OL,8,Fcommunity, working with researchers,
OL,9,Fdetected microfibre and microparticle
OL,10,Fpollution at every site sampled in
OL,11,Fspring 2025.
OL,13,FMicrofibres, often shed from clothing,
OL,14,Fdominated the samples, while
OL,15,Ffibreglass was also present, together
OL,16,Fwith tyre particles.
