OL,3,CConcerns raised as tiny plastic and
OL,4,Cfibreglass particles found in River
OL,5,CItchen
OL,7,FThe University of Brighton said this
OL,8,Fcontamination can disrupt the river
OL,9,Fecosystem, posing risks to insects,
OL,10,Ffish and mammals that depend on these
OL,11,Fchalk streams.
OL,13,FEarly analysis suggests this type of
OL,14,Fpollution is widespread across the
OL,15,Fstreams of the Upper Itchen.
OL,17,FThe research is still ongoing and
OL,18,Fadditional samples will be analysed
OL,19,Fthroughout 2025.
