OL,5,CItchen
OL,7,FThe aim is to trace pollution sources,
OL,8,Fassess potential impacts on wildlife,
OL,9,Fand explore ways to reduce harm.
OL,11,FThe final report is expected later
OL,12,Fthis year.
OL,14,FThe project is led by Dr Corina
OL,15,FCiocan, Principal Lecturer at
OL,16,FUniversity of Brighton's School of
OL,17,FApplied Sciences and co-Director of
OL,18,Fthe Centre for Environment and Society
OL,19,Fand Ian Diver, a Director of the UIR
OL,20,FCIC.
