OL,4,Cfibreglass particles found in River
OL,5,CItchen
OL,7,FDr Corina Ciocan said: "Chalk streams
OL,8,Flike the Itchen are unique and often
OL,9,Fcompared to rainforests for their
OL,10,Fbiodiversity.
OL,12,F"Finding microfibres and even
OL,13,Ffibreglass fragments at every site we
OL,14,Fsampled is concerning, but it also
OL,15,Fgives us the evidence we need to act.
OL,17,F"The next step is to identify the
OL,18,Fsources of this pollution and work
OL,19,Fwith local partners to reduce it and
OL,20,Fmitigate the impacts."
