OL,7,FIan Diver added: "The Itchen is one of
OL,8,FEngland's iconic chalk rivers with a
OL,9,Fspecial community of plants and
OL,10,Fanimals, but its ecosystem is
OL,11,Fdeclining.
OL,13,F"These early results show that
OL,14,Fmicroparticle pollution is an issue we
OL,15,Fcannot ignore. There is currently no
OL,16,Fdata on particle pollution in the
OL,17,FUpper Itchen.
