OL,7,F"This project changes that. By
OL,8,Fcombining citizen science with
OL,9,Frigorous analysis, we can fill a vital
OL,10,Fknowledge gap and empower landowners,
OL,11,Fconservationists and communities to
OL,12,Fprotect this river for the future."
OL,14,FThe project is supported by Southern
OL,15,FWater and by the National Lottery
OL,16,FHeritage Fund through the Hampshire &
OL,17,FIsle of Wight Wildlife Trust and
OL,18,FWessex Rivers Trust.
